		<li><a href="#EpisPrinEpisLogi">2.5 Epistemological Principles in Epistemic Logic</a></li>
		<li><a href="#PrinKnowBeli">2.6 Principles of Knowledge and Belief</a></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><a href="#KnowGrou">3. Knowledge in Groups</a>
